title: Invisible But Invaluable | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Invisible But Invaluable | Joel Osteen
description:
When you use your talents to help others rise higher, God will take care of promoting you. You will reap what the seeds you sow into the lives of those around you.

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
